==English==

===Nominal phrase===
'''back door''' 
# The entry to a building or house which is away from the street;
# ''(slang)'' The anus, generally used in reference to anal sex.
===Adjectival phrase===
'''back door''' 
#{{baseball}} The path of a pitch which starts outside and then slides over the plate.
#: ''He has a nasty '''back door''' slider.''

